                              <desc type="PurchaseNote">Purchase note; the name of the original owner has been erased. 
                                 The name of the new owner, <persName role="owner" ref="PRS15384WaldaIyasus"><roleName type="title">Malʾaka Gannat</roleName> Walda ʾIyasus</persName>, seems to be written by <ref type="hand" target="#h4"/>.</desc>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘመልአከ፡ ገነተ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ዘተሠየጦ፡ በንዋዩ። ዘሰረቆ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/></q>
                              <q xml:lang="en">This book is of Malʾaka Gannat Walda ʾIyasus who purchased it with his own money. The one who may steal it…</q>          
